name: Rake -5'0 Magic Peanut Surfboard
description:
Rake Surfboards
Handmade in Torquay.

5'0 x 20.5 x 2 .5
(suit rider 70-80 kg)

clear wet rub fcs

(board in pics is the fixed marine ply fins)

Shipping Australia wide only $50.00

Specs :

Shaped by Adrian Knott

The magic peanut is our model that sits in between a Simmons & 
a Fish. The peanut has a narrower outline than the traditional Mini Simmons style boards but still offers the same speed & drive but with added hold from the quad fin set up. For those who cant get there head around the larger outline of a simmons the peanut is a perfect option for a summer fun board.  .
We have removed the stringer for lightness & flex & beefed the glass job up on the bottom to 6 ounce.
Features :

*Rolled entry 
*Single concave
*Stringerless blank
*6 ounce bottom  /double 4 deck & tail patch
*Clear wetrub finish
*The 5'0 will suit a rider from 70-80 kg

name: Rake - Micro Yolko  Resin Tint Surfboard
description:
Custon Made to order
3-4 weeks 
Full Resin Tint

This compact micro egg is a compressed version of the Yolko Model 
Lots of curves in a super short board features S-Deck , forward belly 
Single from under front foot to double out through the tail 
stringerless for lightness & flex . I have widened the outline to 22"
to compensate for the shorterness & allow this micro hull to generate 
maximum speed on more surface area . Quad fin is the fastest fin set up 
as it reduces drag with the elimination of a regular thruster configuration.
Large round tail for smooth arcing turns.

-Shaped By Adrian Knott

-Glass By Andy Warhurst

-Stringerless Blank

-Glass on Quads

name: Pier Supply Co. - Custom Deluxe Surf Skate Gold Series
description:
Pier Supply Co.
( FREE SHIPPING AUSTRALIA )
Gold Series -All boards are Numbered .
Roll your Bones on a Custom Deluxe  Surf Skate .
The look & feel of a vintage skate with modern trimmings .
These boards are made to carve super tight turns.
Carve the sidewalk, Rip the bowl or slash some banks.
The 26 " Custom Deluxe Model takes you back to the roots of skateboarding with its smaller narrower outline.
Pier Skateboards are Hand shaped from start to finish
out of the finest tasmanian oak.
All Completes are set up using the highest quality components & hardware , the under carriage gets some classic re-issue 85mm Tracker Dart trucks which were designed in the 70's ,designed to offer the wheels maximum clearance from the deck ( less chance of wheel bite) these trucks offer a super classic surf feel & allow tight turns at high speeds. The boards are polished off with a set of Cadillac wheels 56 mm 78 Duro

Available in Oak & Maple 

Dimensions : L 26 " X W 7 " 

Finish : Clear Acrylic Sealer

Wheels & Trucks : Tracker 85mm Dart Trucks & cadillac 56 mm wheels
